graphql.query:
query GetRangeofLedgers  {
  blockRange(sBlock: 50807533, lBlock: 50807544) {
    seqno
    shard
    workchain
    rootHash
    fileHash
    transactions {
      isAborted
      isDestroyed
      transactionHash
      blockSeqNumber
      blockWorkchain
      blockShard
      account
      fee
      timestamp
      isTokenTransfer
      contractAddress
      inMessage {
        source
        destination
        amount
        opcode
        blockSeqNumber
        transactionHash
        hash
        comment
      }
      outMessage {
        source
        destination
        amount
        opcode
        blockSeqNumber
        transactionHash
        hash
        comment
      }
    }
  }
}
